node.text: @itsnicethat asked me to take part in their #creativeresolution2020 instagram brief! my new year's resolution is to manage my time more effectively and try to become a more efficient person. this is an open thing, anyone can upload their creative resolution artwork to instagram with the #CreativeResolution2020 hashtag and @itsnicethat will share their favourite submissions in the new year. you can find out more on their profile.

this riso print from print show II at @likelygeneral is now available for purchase from @colourcodeprint! it's a collage that i split into sunflower, mint, raspberry, and hunter green. i haven’t shared a lot of collage work here but it’s one of my favourite mediums and i really like this piece.
